    dc:description "Fig. 4. Gulella judithmastersae sp. nov., holotype (NMSA-Mol 0P2354/T4603), length 3.4 mm, width 1.6 mm. A. Aperture view. B. Side view. C. Detail of aperture. D. Oblique view of base showing umbilicus." ;
